    <item>
      <title>What Enchanters Really Need</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Enchanters&amp;message.id=4624#M4624</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;I have read and Posted on several messages throughout the board concerning the class envisionment and this is what in my mind I believe actually needs to be done to save this dieing class.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Charm - reduce the DPS by no more than 50%,do not make these pets hasted/buffed in any way,but make charm more stable.With TD3 and 340 Charisma I still have charm breaks after 1 tic - this is wrong.If you want to reduce the dps on charmed mobs below this proposed 50%,then make all charms fixed duration,with Total Domination adding 1 minute per rank to the charm duration.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Upgrade Dire Charm through use of AA's - currently we are able to DC a mob to max level 46 - this is useless in the higher end game when enchanters are forced to solo because other classes are more needed in groups.Increase the DC level by 2 levels per rank up to a max of lvl 52 ( this is only 3 ranks)and make the AA cost moderate like 5-10-15 AA's per level rank.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Make Illusions useful,with their own built in collaboration type effect so they are more useable for entering cities,doing quests.Upgrade certain Illusions like BoG,NDT,Tricksters,placing them more in line with todays content and making them more desirable.Make our Illusions more usefull as well - certain effects like HP regen,attack rating,strength,dex,etc., that increases with the level of the caster.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Slows - A slow that is on par or slightly below that of a shamans.A fast cast low resist slow like they have will make us more desireable in groups.Low resist so we dont have to pre cast Tash - shamans dont need tash or malo on their slows so why do we?&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Nukes that do more than agrivate a mob.Our best nuke tops out at 3k+ with a critical strike.Toss us a bone and seriously upgrade some nukes and DoTs for us.We should have a 2k nuke minimum and DoTs that do not get overwritten by everything a necro casts.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Upgrade our Stun line of spells not WoM.Morrel is a PBAoE MEZZ.Mezz = aggro. AoE Aggro = death.Upgrade Whirl Till You Hurl,Color stuns,Lagarn's Lamentation.We need more single target stuns not PBAoE mezz's that last for 6 seconds,7 for the enchanter when he dies 1 second after it breaks.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Lower resists on mezzes.The chances of a mezz being resisted in the higher end game is too high and chanters are often plastered to a wall when multiple mobs are coming into camp.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Make Mezz the first spells gained for rune turn ins for OoW spells.Increase drop rate again on greater and glowing runes - these are no drop anyway so they cannot be sold off and screw up eq economy.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Upgrade Tash - long overdue again considering who MR mobs are against magic based spells.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Upgrade our personal rune spell to enable us to take more than 1 hit from a top end mob.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;New Ideas - &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Give enchanters the ability to feed mana to others like Necros do - we have been the means for mana regen and controlling the mind since EQ started and how this ability has been overlooked for 6 years is beyond me.Considering how useless we have become on raids,the least we can do is give our mana to others when a mana draining mob is encountered.Give enchanters also the ability to resist mana drain spells slightly better than other classes - we can control the mind,and therefore should be able to resist a mob being able to drain our mana.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Give us a line of spells that will make us more usefull in groups - similar to clerics with the abilities to speed up spell casting,reduce fizzling even more,even make others spells more effective.Perhaps even give us the ability to reduce the mana cost of others with certain group-only abilities/buffs.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Spells that enable us to enchant weapons/armor and make them more effective.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Haste spell that breaks haste cap.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Buffs that can break the stat cap on certain stats like intell and wisdom.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;One suggestion I even saw was the best idea I have seen in years.Increase the hp/ac of enchanters to be on par with that of a druid while keeping us in cloth armor.Considering how fast an enchanter dies when charm breaks or mezz is resisted,this plan seems to be the most feasible.No other arcane caster class faces the aggro we do from certain spells that need to be cast while in group - and this is one of the reasons chanters are overlooked.No group wants to constantly rezz an enchanter who is grabbing aggro with tash,slow,cripple,or charm,and is having to be babysat with constant heals.Raising our ac to make us get hit less often,and hp to make us take more damage when we do grab aggro will make other classes fell safer knowing we wont need a rezz every 3 minutes.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;These suggestions on things we need could be expanded upon im am sure,but these seem to be the most needed items to keep this class from dieing off.We have become useless buffbots and I dare an EQ dev to log into any server and look for themselves as to how many enchanters are actually in groups.We are few and far between now,and our usefullness is currently limited to helping get people flagged on trials 5 and 6 for KT.This will change with upcoming plans to charm,and our class will not be needed at all for that - face it - we cant take a hit and we will be passed up for dps classes to take out the mobs faster.And taking out a mob with speed is not something an enchanter is able to do considering the nukes and dots we have.Charm was what gave us an edge and that has been nerfed to hell and back and will now be totally useless.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Pre 60 chanters have a chance at finding groups as the spells for our class was designed for that type of content - but from 60 to 70 it seems as though SOE hired a bunch of monkeys with computer skills to toss us some random crap every now and then.The 60-70 spells and our abilities do not match the content in the game,especially since OoW and DoN arrived.LDoN gave us a few spells that were useful,but LDoN is a thing of the past for post 60 toons now that better gear and content is available with DoN.LoY was a running joke offering us 1 spell that is moderately useful,but those zones also are dead as the content and gear coming from there is outdated.The risk vs. reward does not warrant many groups going there and is subject to many soloing classes over groups for the fact camps arent in dispute.GoD offered us some nice rewards providing we were already Time geared to face the mobs to get it.The spells in GoD were way out of balance when it is considered what level you need to be to get them,compared with the level of spell you recieved.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;The game for many post 60 enchanters starts to go downhill after they hit the Planes and get flagged for the elemental zones and Time.As more guilds move into the raid content for GoD,OoW,and DoN,enchanters are having a hard time finding their niche considering how useless our spells have become compared to that of other classes.We recieve nerfs but no upgrades to what is useful and needed to keep us in groups.The spells and abilities we were given pre 60 made us wanted - now we take up space on raids and groups that is more needed for actual dps classes that can make or break a successful run.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;We need a serious overhaul,and our abilities need to be looked at closely when you compare the pre and post 60 enchanter.&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
