eed them against the Resists you have imposed since OoW.........no way should we not have abilities to avoid splatting in 1 round to any blue-con mobs in a group environment - btw I may not have max AA's for Defensiveness yet, but I am fairly close, and tire of splatting to blues because I do not see the defenses happening as I think they should with the number of AA's I have already trained....this is with 8K raid buffed hp and epic rune, ethereal rune, mayhem, and rune of Z accounted for as buffs ~ 12k hp +/-.........no its not poor healers in group (I group and raid with these healers and they are very high quality healers).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Im at the point in game, if I can't find a group with the folks I know and trust, I seldom stay online more than an hour looking for other friends to group with...........and I am one who used to play up to 10+ hours daily, now down to maybe 4 hours for raiding 4-5 nights a week only.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;So, I will be waiting for answers for a short while longer.</description>
